::::::::::Datasets and settings::::::::::
**********Datasets***********************
Refer to twiki: https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMSPublic/WorkBookMiniAOD
DATA: Re-Reco-BCDEFG+PromptReco-H (will be changed in next iteration for Moriond17)
MC: RunIISpring16MiniAODv2-PUSpring16_80X_mcRun2_asymptotic_2016_miniAODv2_v0/MINIAODSIM
(The MC sample right now recommended are Spring16 ones, however, for Moriond17, the recommended are Summer16 samples which will be used later on 
when these will be asked and recommended to use.)
***********Global tags*******************
Refer to twiki: https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMSPublic/WorkBookMiniAOD
DATA GT: 80X_dataRun2_2016SeptRePro_v4
MC GT: 80X_mcRun2_asymptotic_2016_miniAODv2

