**********JetEnergyCorrections***********
Refer to twiki: https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/JECDataMC
The jet energy corrections used in this set is : Spring16_23Sep2016AllV2_DATA for data
and Spring16_25nsV10_MC for MC using sqlite files.
This will be updated further and will have to be changed accordingly.
Email for announcement: https://mmm.cern.ch/owa/?ae=Item&a=Open&t=IPM.Note&id=RgAAAAAVYcc7ugiYQoBqvGptA5XEBwCB90QqZNMdSZ%2fbaeqz89oLAAAAsIwBAACB90QqZNMdSZ%2fbaeqz89oLAADX84YBAAAJ&pspid=_1483510466997_759537586

