*********Photon energy scale and resolution*****
Refer to twiki: https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/EGMSmearer

The code including it is updated in CMSSW_8_0_24_patch1
However, these corrections are still for ICHEP and will be updated.

*********Solution for Slew-Rate problem in photons*****
The solution for this is given in EGMSmearer twiki under section: ECAL scale and resolution corrections for Moriond 2017 (preliminary version)
under NOTE.
I have added these corrections also in CMSSW_8_0_24_patch1. and made two new branches with these corrections.

